<D>__{i figured that would get your attention.. i did the same thing to ghandi, he couldn't eat for three weeks. now, here's the deal. you have all my power. use it any way you choose. there are only two rules. you can't tell anyone you're god. believe me you don't want that kind of attention. and you can't mess with free will.}
<C>__{bruce}
<D>__{uh huh. can i ask why?}
